description: Enter into a gracious foyer with adjacent powder room. Gorgeous limestone floors in all formal living spaces. Unique one of a kind floorplan has family room kitchen, great for casual living & entertaining. Kitchen has top of the line appliances & island. Formal living room, dining room offers spectacular views of lake & city, features gas fireplace. 2 ensuite bedrooms with guest bedroom bath totally redone. This home is in pristine condition. Building sits atop of the Flagship Hyatt Hotel with hotel amenities at your finger tips. 800 has on site manager, assistant manager, 2 doormen, receiving room, & engineers. 1 garage space included.
